message.body: Hey. Just so you know, I sent you $58. I had it down in my records that I owed you it. $30 for when we ate at Alfa. $8 for pizza. And $20 for miscellaneo
us things I don't remember. Let me know when you get it.
Really? I totally forgot, lol Thanks.
Haha I know. It's a good things I write these things down.
By the way, I should be in town on the 25th to the 27th.
